WEBVTT

1
00:00:13.166 --> 00:00:14.566
What are you doing here?

2
00:00:14.566 --> 00:00:17.466
Brother-in-law, we are here to apologize to you and sister

3
00:00:17.466 --> 00:00:18.566
We know wrong.

4
00:00:18.566 --> 00:00:20.066
Please forgive us

5
00:00:20.333 --> 00:00:21.300
Yes, brother-in-law.

6
00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:22.100
You can't always

7
00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:24.166
Don't even give us a chance to change

8
00:00:24.166 --> 00:00:25.033
Right?

9
00:00:25.766 --> 00:00:27.500
Ok, I forgive you.

10
00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:28.766
Now get out

11
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.566
Brother-in-law, we sincerely regret it.

12
00:00:32.566 --> 00:00:34.000
Don't be angry.

13
00:00:34.300 --> 00:00:35.200
Yes, brother-in-law.

14
00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:36.900
You see, we're all family.

15
00:00:36.900 --> 00:00:38.500
Broken bones and tendons

16
00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:40.566
Besides, you own so many properties

17
00:00:40.566 --> 00:00:42.400
You can't rest assured if you hand it over to outsiders.

18
00:00:42.400 --> 00:00:43.333
You leave it to me

19
00:00:43.333 --> 00:00:45.033
I'll take care of it for you for free.

20
00:00:45.466 --> 00:00:47.100
That's the idea

21
00:00:47.933 --> 00:00:49.866
I don't think you're here to apologize at all

22
00:00:51.266 --> 00:00:54.066
Xiaoyu, how did you treat your sister in the past?

23
00:00:54.066 --> 00:00:55.500
You know it.

24
00:00:55.533 --> 00:00:58.766
And you, as Jiang Yuning's boyfriend

25
00:00:58.766 --> 00:01:00.400
Not only unchecked

26
00:01:00.800 --> 00:01:02.100
Instead, help the curse

27
00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:04.400
If I were powerless

28
00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:06.166
Don't you let you bully

